<p>Extend Zend\Uri\Uri with a Iri class that can validate according to the RFC3987 spec.</p>

<p>Requesting this since HTML5 Url element uses RFC3986 and RFC3987 for the browser validation, and it would be nice to have same validations on the server.</p>

